### Register a New User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test-player@nightcity.com",
  "password": "supersecurepassword",
  "avatarName": "CyberRunner"
}

### Login existing user
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test-player@nightcity.com",
  "password": "supersecurepassword"
}